{"tid":649262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[厲害了，我的國] 習近平將接見美方貿易團 中方或作讓步","createTime":"2018-05-01T11:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T07:43:21.000Z","uid":54733,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5547be883e0df7fd5bf423e9d0d75cbae8a68c","tid":649262,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》報道，中國將以高規格接待周四開始訪華的美國貿易代表團，國家主席習近平將親自接見美方官員，北京亦有意承諾削減關稅，以及放寬貿易規例，甚至作出更多友善行動，最終尋求化解兩國的貿易爭端。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普本周將派出代表團訪問中國，商討中美貿易關係，代表團成員包括財長努欽、貿易代表萊特海澤、白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅、國家經濟顧問委員會總監庫德洛等，預期周四抵達北京。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，中美兩國官員今次的會面注定是一場高風險談判。美方對中國將作出多大承諾仍抱持懷疑態度，因此計劃採取強硬立場。美方今次有違常態，在訪問北京前並無派遣先遣人員前往中國進行初步談判，而是打算在會面時，直接抛出特朗普擬徵收關稅的威脅，並向中方作出投訴，這種談判策略具相當危險性，若然成功可望推動中國深化經濟改革，但若策略不收效，或導致兩國的敵意加深。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，貿易代表團為雙方緩解緊張局勢提供了機會，但快速解決問題的機會相信很渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室依據「301調查」結果，於本月3日建議對來自中國價值約500億美元進口商品加徵25%的關稅，主要涉及訊息和通訊技術、航天航空、機械人、醫藥、機械等行業。中方認為美國的指控毫無依據。"},{"pid":"f24795a134619bf88646b0f22efbb90cdacc6b3e","tid":649262,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:50:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1831594/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%3A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%9C%98+%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%88%96%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1831594%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%253A%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%259C%2598%2B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%25AD%25A5&d=DsxdYVgv1v6SLJVdYobZ%2BDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0993c06e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1831594/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%3A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%9C%98+%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%88%96%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5</a>"},{"pid":"2d698b0123ee5bad7d63d0813ad7958c08ca52e0","tid":649262,"uid":67468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4b58a4167dae3d036e4c07808c197c98227876","tid":649262,"uid":42188,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"中國或成最後贏家"},{"pid":"cfbb9f820c64eea48519833866ff4d198e79bd85","tid":649262,"uid":54733,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"同場加映:<br />\n<br />\n美中貿易戰中國外交部：有信心笑到最後<br />\n<br />\n針對美中貿易戰，中國外交部發言人耿爽今天說，希望美方「不要誤判形勢、心存幻想，不要在錯誤的道路上越走越遠」。中國人「向來說到做到」，「我們有信心笑到最後」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2390235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2390235&d=DsxdYVgv1v6SLJVdYobZ%2BDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=223a86d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2390235&h=91fa3e66\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2390235</a>"},{"pid":"6b0891b0444d7985c59d77e61396f5235d792a4c","tid":649262,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:52:51.000Z","msg":"又贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5037aee7755beb7e75e6488d59a2906efdc832","tid":649262,"uid":31389,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"亮劍啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f0817381c73247517b437c7aae46eb3f7d9db8","tid":649262,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal